{"tid":2114662,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英日同盟：英國邀日本參與當地5G建設取代華為！","createTime":"2020-07-19T04:18:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T16:01:55.000Z","uid":111253,"like":60,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"316f537868e223f88654162b0a7e2ef93ec69c88","tid":2114662,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:18:47.000Z","msg":"《日經亞洲評論》披露，英國政府已發出邀請，要求日本廠商參與當地5G無線網絡建設。英國官員隨即於本月16日會見日本政府的代表，包括國家安全保障會議（NSC）和國家安全資訊中心（NISC）在內，英方向日方尋求5G技術合作，希望如NEC和富士通（Fujitsu）等日企能夠取代華為作為5G設備的供應商。"},{"pid":"023871b12abed34a5dbf4b1f314cdc79bd493a84","tid":2114662,"uid":111253,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:19:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u18f5VZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu18f5VZ.jpg&h=00addf55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0bca3878a79179f279f837c81feed9543cfc59ae","tid":2114662,"uid":128600,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:19:47.000Z","msg":"基本法呢? 石頭呢? 腳呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d41cef289b426338499a52bb99e604dd69587677","tid":2114662,"uid":104138,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:20:15.000Z","msg":"日本重收漁人之利<br />\n唔知安培點諗呢"},{"pid":"2b5246abbfb657ef981c9a3501fe94defe6b9823","tid":2114662,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:20:30.000Z","msg":"遼寧號到入咗北海未？"},{"pid":"7e030a82f330f0c89af406c5843d6575ede80a99","tid":2114662,"uid":51583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:20:36.000Z","msg":"五眼加日台組個聯盟可以好屈機<br />\n搵多幾個信得過既國家一齊玩已經夠晒"},{"pid":"e9455d0f503896ef6292874a5ad30bec82bdeffa","tid":2114662,"uid":321977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"023871b12abed34a5dbf4b1f314cdc79bd493a84","tid":2114662,"uid":111253,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:19:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u18f5VZ.jpg